methods.binMax:
Gets the max value of the bin at rowSet.

:param index: (long) - rowSet
:return: (double) max value of the bin specified by rowSet
methods.binMin:
Gets the min value of the bin at rowSet.

:param index: (long) - rowSet
:return: (double) min value of the bin specified by rowSet
methods.index:
Gets the rowSet of the bin the value lies in.

:param value: (double) - value
:return: (long) max value of the bin specified by rowSet

text: DiscretizedRange where all bins are equal length.
